text: Jörg Urban (2019) Jörg Urban (born 4 August 1964) is a German politician for the Alternative for Germany and member of the Landtag of the Free State of Saxony since 2014. ==Life and politics== Urban was born 1964 in Meißen and is a skilled hydraulic engineer. In 2013, Urban became member of the AfD and is the chairman of the parliamentary group of his party in the federal state of Saxony. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Alternative for Germany politicians Category:Members of the Landtag of Saxony Category:People from Meissen Category:Living people
title: Jörg Urban
